00:03:37,805 --> 00:03:40,096
Dia akan menjemputku di Yongsan
dan membawaku ke terminal.

29
00:03:40,179 --> 00:03:43,179
Kalian bertemu di Yongsan,
kenapa pergi ke terminal?

30
00:03:43,262 --> 00:03:45,054
Jika ingin tahu, ikutlah.

31
00:03:45,137 --> 00:03:47,513
Aku tak bisa ikut. Butuh berapa lama?

32
00:03:47,596 --> 00:03:49,346
Dua jam, katanya.

33
00:03:51,054 --> 00:03:52,553
Dua jam...

