Hei, jaga sikapmu.

45
00:04:18,177 --> 00:04:19,678
Duduklah lagi.

46
00:04:21,552 --> 00:04:23,052
Kau mau hamburger?

47
00:04:23,135 --> 00:04:24,803
Kini kau baru bertanya?

48
00:04:26,177 --> 00:04:27,344
Kembalilah!

49
00:04:35,010 --> 00:04:39,760
