51
00:04:43,635 --> 00:04:45,677
<i>Setelah mendirikan Ewoo Shipping,</i>

52
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:48,593
<i>Lee mendorong perekonomian Korea
di era 1980-an,</i>

53
00:04:48,677 --> 00:04:51,676
