237
00:19:11,843 --> 00:19:13,135
Seo Young-rak.

238
00:19:14,135 --> 00:19:16,968
Kudengar ibumu memanggilmu "Rak".

239
00:19:17,052 --> 00:19:19,134
Bolehkah kupanggil begitu juga?

240
00:19:19,843 --> 00:19:21,384
Tuan Lee itu siapa?

241
00:19:25,384 --> 00:19:26,384
Baik.

