388
00:31:17,766 --> 00:31:18,766
Belajarlah dari aku.

389
00:31:22,225 --> 00:31:23,725
Nona!

390
00:31:27,433 --> 00:31:29,683
Kau benar-benar cantik.

391
00:31:29,766 --> 00:31:33,349
Berwajah aktris, tapi bertubuh model.

392
00:31:34,099 --> 00:31:36,849
