00:35:45,296 --> 00:35:48,587
maka Leica ini klasik dan berat.

439
00:36:46,501 --> 00:36:47,585
Apa pendapatmu?

440
00:37:13,083 --> 00:37:14,167
Pak.

441
00:37:14,791 --> 00:37:17,000
Bagaimana prosedur pengambilan
bahan mentahnya?

442
00:37:35,790 --> 00:37:40,748
