685
01:01:28,805 --> 01:01:30,138
Direktur Brian datang.

686
01:01:30,222 --> 01:01:31,597
Itu yang Park katakan.

687
01:01:32,514 --> 01:01:33,721
Brian?

688
01:01:55,096 --> 01:01:57,804
Sapalah. Ini Brian.

689
01:02:01,470 --> 01:02:02,553
Dia tak terdaftar.

690
01:02:04,095 --> 01:02:05,720
Seo Young-rak.

691
01:02:08,261 --> 01:02:10,470
Kau marah, bukan?

692
01:02:11,720 --> 01:02:14,803
Kau berduka, murka,

693
