694
01:02:20,220 --> 01:02:23,677
Memang seharusnya begitu.
Kau telah mengalami masa sulit.

695
01:02:24,594 --> 01:02:25,761
Itu wajar.

696
01:02:28,594 --> 01:02:31,636
Kau beragama apa, Tuan Seo?

697
01:02:33,344 --> 01:02:34,344
Jawab dia.

698
01:02:34,968 --> 01:02:36,385
Tak apa-apa.

699
01:02:36,469 --> 01:02:39,344
Kau bisa mulai dengan memercayai satu hal.

700
01:02:39,426 --> 01:02:41,010
"Hendaklah ia meminta dalam iman,

701
01:02:41,927 --> 01:02:44,426
