<i>Ya, Pak?</i>

713
01:04:49,171 --> 01:04:52,420
Tentang Seo Young-rak.

714
01:04:52,504 --> 01:04:54,504
<i>Aku minta maaf atas perilakunya.</i>

715
01:04:54,587 --> 01:04:56,128
