748
01:07:29,621 --> 01:07:31,330
Jika kita depak dia sekarang, mungkin...

749
01:07:45,204 --> 01:07:46,662
Mari kita...

750
01:07:50,370 --> 01:07:51,745
berdoa bersama.

751
01:07:58,536 --> 01:07:59,787
Pak... Kumohon...

752
01:08:24,494 --> 01:08:26,744
Apa-apaan ini?

753
01:08:29,910 --> 01:08:31,160
Tuan Park.

754
01:08:33,493 --> 01:08:36,743
Sudah berapa kali kukatakan padamu?
Apa pun yang terjadi,

755
01:08:36,826 --> 01:08:39,493
jangan menemuiku di sini.

756
01:08:39,576 --> 01:08:40,576
Benar?

757
01:08:41,618 --> 01:08:44,242
Jika aturan dasar ini tak ditegakkan,

758
01:08:45,159 --> 01:08:49,534
